      "body" : "There is a limit - currently 100 IIRC, though I would vote for the option to change that in the GUI options menu.\r\nSetting it lower is something that would have to be thoroughly discussed first.  As I mentioned, the network is already starved of nodes which accept incoming connections, limiting that number further could have very serious consequences.  Someone needs to do some analysis of the network, but until then, the max connection limit really shouldnt be touched IMO.",
